                                 the Recrypt Mode, the Cipher Block Chaining Mode (CBC-MAC), the CBC-MAC- encrypt-
                                 last-block (CBC-MAC-ELB) mode and cryptographic key sizes of 128 bit or 192 bit or 256
                                 bit that meet the following standards:

